"Gwelell Profil Liw GNOME diskwedhes profilys liw leys war dha system ha gasa "
"ty alinya skrinyow, pryntyoryon ha kameras ow devnydhya pystrier."

#: data/appdata/org.gnome.ColorProfileViewer.metainfo.xml.in:19
