"This functionality is typically used by GNOME Control Center from the color "
"panel although can be used on its own."
msgstr ""
"An nas yw devnydhys dell yw usys gans Kresen Routyans GNOME dhyworth an "
"panel liw kynth a yll bos devnydhys yn unsel."

